snippet.title: Party Club Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Manage your venue, seat customers, serve drinks, kick the messy customers, survive disasters, and celebrate festivals. Party Club offers you a Co-Op experience with up to 4 players!

Features
Online and Local Co-Op
Venue Arrangement
Unlock new regions by completing quests
Character Customization
Greet, seat, and serve customers

But most importantly don't forget to have fun!
